---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Faith Nte - Fractional SEO Consultant"
  description="Meet Faith Nte, Fractional SEO Consultant specializing in healthcare and private practice growth"
>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-50 to-stone-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Content -->
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6"
            >
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-neutral-600 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
              Fractional SEO Consultant
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
              Hi, I'm Faith Nte
            </h1>

            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              I help healthcare professionals and private practice owners build
              sustainable growth through strategic SEO and web design that
              converts visitors into patients.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a
                href="https://outlook.office.com/book/Free30MinsConsultation@faithnte.com/"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-800 to-black text-white rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Book Free Consultation
                <svg
                  class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://fenn.digital"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-neutral-300 text-neutral-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-50 hover:border-neutral-400 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Visit Fenn Digital
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Profile Image -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative w-80 h-80 mx-auto">
              <img
                src="/faithnte.svg"
                alt="Faith Nte - Fractional SEO Consultant"
                class="w-full h-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-2xl"
              />
              <!-- Decorative elements -->
              <div
                class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-neutral-100 rounded-full opacity-60"
              >
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-stone-100 rounded-full opacity-60"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <!-- About Section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About My Approach</h2>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            As founder of <a
              href="https://fenn.digital"
              class="text-neutral-700 hover:text-black font-medium border-b border-neutral-300 hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors"
              target="_blank">Fenn Digital</a
            >, I specialise in helping healthcare professionals and private
            practice owners build sustainable growth. Clinicians should be able
            to focus on caring for their patients, not wrestling with marketing.
            That's why I work with you to create a website and SEO strategy that
            connects you with your ideal clients and consistently brings in
            bookings.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            My approach combines web design and growth marketing, honed through
            years of experience with private practices and digital
            transformation projects in the NHS. At Fenn Digital we build
            websites that are <strong>"SEO‑ready from day one,"</strong> with clear,
            trustworthy designs and quick turnarounds. I lead the marketing strategy,
            working closely with designers to deliver sites that attract, engage
            and convert.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Highlight -->
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-50 to-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16 border border-neutral-200"
      >
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Freedom-15 Package
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          If you're a therapist, coach or other healthcare specialist who wants
          simple, effective marketing instead of a £5k website, my <strong
            >"Freedom‑15" package</strong
          > may be right for you.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://fenn.digital"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-neutral-700 hover:text-black font-semibold border-b border-neutral-300 hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Learn more about Freedom-15
          <svg
            class="ml-1 w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Results Section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Proven Results</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-neutral-700"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 ml-4">
                Traffic Growth
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Transformed a safety‑deposit‑box blog from <strong
                >20 monthly visitors to 7,000</strong
              > and achieved a <strong>#1 UK ranking</strong>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-stone-700"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 ml-4">
                Patient Bookings
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              For Dr J & Colleagues, boosted website traffic from <strong
                >300 to 8,000</strong
              > monthly visitors and increased patient bookings by <strong
                >30%</strong
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Grow Your Practice?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Let's build a website that gets you found, connects you with the right
          people and frees you to focus on what matters most.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://outlook.office.com/book/Free30MinsConsultation@faithnte.com/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-800 to-black text-white rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-lg"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Book Your Free Consultation
          <svg
            class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
